response.original_title: ONE Championship 109: King of the Jungle
response.overview: This MMA event was held in Singapore on 28th February 2020. It had a total of 11 fights.  Headlining the event is two-sport ONE World Champion, Stamp Fairtex, who defends her ONE Atomweight Kickboxing World Title against Janet Todd in an epic rematch. Plus, ONE Strawweight Kickboxing World Champion Sam-A Gaiyanghadao takes on Aussie phenom Rocky Ogden for the inaugural ONE Strawweight Muay Thai World Championship.
response.title: ONE Championship 109: King of the Jungle
